<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="play-a-trick-on-sb">play a trick on sb.</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>捉弄某人，对某人恶作剧</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If the neighbours do not give any sweets, the children might play a trick on them.
如果邻居们不给糖果，孩子们就可以捉弄他们。</p><footer>人教③ – 1</footer></div></div>